<title>SUI KHUALIPI CH440</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thihnak tiva ral ah khin khuadawh cu a um, A sunparnak chim khawh lomi
 cu, Khika'h ni a tla lo, thinghnah zong a uai lo, Cu sui khuapi dawh le
 nuam ah cun.

[C1]
   Khika ni, a tla lo, Thinghnah zong a uai lo, Khi ka'h mithiang mi
   nih, An Khamhtu an hmuh lai, Cu sui khuapi dawh le nuam ah cun.

[V2]
 Khika ah kan dawt Bawipa a kan tlantu cu, A zummi nih lawm in kan hmuh
 lai, Zungzal in van arfi hna bang in kan ceu lai, Cu sui khuapi dawh le
 nuam ah cun.

[C2]
   Khika ni, a tla lo, Thinghnah zong a uai lo, Khi ka'h mithiang mi
   nih, An Khamhtu an hmuh lai, Cu sui khuapi dawh le nuam ah cun.

[V3]
 Vai-lamtah hram kan phak pimi thlarau vialte, Kan hmuhmi tuufa vialte
 hna hi, Kan sui luchin dawhter tu cu an si te lai, Cu sui khuapi dawh le
 nuam ah cun.

[C3]
   Khika ni, a tla lo, Thinghnah zong a uai lo, Khi ka'h mithiang mi
   nih, An Khamhtu an hmuh lai, Cu sui khuapi dawh le nuam ah cun.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>